Description: Tomoko Kuroki comes to a harsh realization when she begins high school: she's horribly unpopular!
Title: NO MATTER HOW I LOOK AT IT, IT'S YOU GUYS' FAULT I'M NOT POPULAR!, VOL. 3
Author: Nico Tanigawa

Description: In the not–too–distant future, a popular virtual reality video game traps its users, so the only way to log out is to beat the game. But if they die in the virtual world, it also means “game over” in the real world!
Title: SWORD ART ONLINE: AINCRAD
Author: Reki Kawahara and Tamako Nakamura
Contributor: by Reki Kawahara and Tamako Nakamura

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The magical beast Ten Tails has awoken and only Naruto and the Allied Shinobi Forces stand in its way!
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 65
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Ririchiyo Shirakiin has moved into a secured apartment building to gain some privacy, but her parents have arranged for a bodyguard named Soushi to protect her and he won't leave her alone!
Title: INU X BOKU SS, VOL. 3
Author: Cocoa Fujiwara

Description: Ezra faces not one but two of the most powerful female wizards in the world while Natsu barrels ahead with his reckless plan to rescue Lucy.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 37
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: Hana meets and falls in love with a man who is a werewolf, but when tragedy strikes, she is forced to raise their children alone in this adaptation of the animated film.
Title: WOLF CHILDREN: AME AND YUKI
Author: Mamoru Hosoda and Yu

Description: Welcome to Academy City, which teems with psychics. One of them is Mikoto Misaka, who investigates the dark side of things.
Title: A CERTAIN SCIENTIFIC RAILGUN, VOL. 9
Author: Kazuma Kamachi and Motoi Fuyukawa
Contributor: by Kazuma Kamachi and Motoi Fuyukawa

Description: William Twining is a poor realist who cannot pay for his school tuition. That is, until demons start to suddenly appear before him, offering their financial assistance.
Title: DEVILS AND REALIST, VOL. 1
Author: Madoka Takadono and Utako Yukihiro
Contributor: by Madoka Takadono and Utako Yukihiro

Description: Mankind has gone into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans. In this volume, what happens when a human boy becomes a Titan?
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 3
Author: Hajime Isayama
